{"ID":"20220906203817-q189139","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220906203817-q189139","title":"b-3Java多线程","type":"doc","updated":"20220906203817"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203818-ftlcnxc","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20220906203818-ftlcnxc","updated":"20220906203818"}},{"ID":"20220906203819-ifgfa8a","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203819-ifgfa8a","updated":"20220906203819"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.3. 多线程","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203820-teilwrz","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906203820-teilwrz","updated":"20220906203820"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906203821-0knhzne","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203821-0knhzne","updated":"20220906203821"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/","TextMarkTextContent":"JavaGuide"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：「Java学习+面试指南」一份涵盖大部分 Java 程序员所需要掌握的核心知识。准备 Java 面试，首选 JavaGuide！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203822-i75lhwh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203822-i75lhwh","updated":"20220906203822"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这部分内容摘自 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/","TextMarkTextContent":"JavaGuide"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 下面几篇文章：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203823-zevxd8q","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203823-zevxd8q","updated":"20220906203823"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203824-sxzexsw","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203824-sxzexsw","updated":"20220906203824"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203825-wxd3zi4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203825-wxd3zi4","updated":"20220906203825"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/java/concurrent/java-concurrent-questions-01.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Java 并发常见面试题总结（上）"}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203826-3kqkjvs","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203826-3kqkjvs","updated":"20220906203826"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203827-lp9s7vu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203827-lp9s7vu","updated":"20220906203827"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/java/concurrent/java-concurrent-questions-02.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Java 并发常见面试题总结（中）"}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203828-mfg3vfy","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203828-mfg3vfy","updated":"20220906203828"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203829-skhgalf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203829-skhgalf","updated":"20220906203829"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/java/concurrent/java-concurrent-questions-03.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Java 并发常见面试题总结（下）"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203830-q2mkjq3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203830-q2mkjq3","updated":"20220906203830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是线程和进程?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203831-2wxi9gh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203831-2wxi9gh","updated":"20220906203831"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何为进程?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203832-ounhbd5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203832-ounhbd5","updated":"20220906203832"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进程是程序的一次执行过程，是系统运行程序的基本单位，因此进程是动态的。系统运行一个程序即是一个进程从创建，运行到消亡的过程。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203833-61hs8yr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203833-61hs8yr","updated":"20220906203833"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在 Java 中，当我们启动 main 函数时其实就是启动了一个 JVM 的进程，而 main 函数所在的线程就是这个进程中的一个线程，也称主线程。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203834-4g7awnp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203834-4g7awnp","updated":"20220906203834"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如下图所示，在 Windows 中通过查看任务管理器的方式，我们就可以清楚看到 Windows 当前运行的进程（","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":".exe"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 文件的运行）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203835-1nxhaah","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203835-1nxhaah","updated":"20220906203835"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"进程示例图片-Windows","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://my-blog-to-use.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/2019-6/进程示例图片-Windows.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203836-hw2ypvm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203836-hw2ypvm","updated":"20220906203836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何为线程?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203837-m6cyoao","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203837-m6cyoao","updated":"20220906203837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程与进程相似，但线程是一个比进程更小的执行单位。一个进程在其执行的过程中可以产生多个线程。与进程不同的是同类的多个线程共享进程的","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"堆"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"方法区"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"资源，但每个线程有自己的","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"程序计数器"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚拟机栈"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"本地方法栈"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，所以系统在产生一个线程，或是在各个线程之间作切换工作时，负担要比进程小得多，也正因为如此，线程也被称为轻量级进程。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203838-vfrv64m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203838-vfrv64m","updated":"20220906203838"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Java 程序天生就是多线程程序，我们可以通过 JMX 来看看一个普通的 Java 程序有哪些线程，代码如下。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203839-jugi3hj","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906203839-jugi3hj","updated":"20220906203839"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"public class MultiThread {\n\tpublic static void main(String[] args) {\n\t\t// 获取 Java 线程管理 MXBean\n\tThreadMXBean threadMXBean = ManagementFactory.getThreadMXBean();\n\t\t// 不需要获取同步的 monitor 和 synchronizer 信息，仅获取线程和线程堆栈信息\n\t\tThreadInfo[] threadInfos = threadMXBean.dumpAllThreads(false, false);\n\t\t// 遍历线程信息，仅打印线程 ID 和线程名称信息\n\t\tfor (ThreadInfo threadInfo : threadInfos) {\n\t\t\tSystem.out.println(\"[\" + threadInfo.getThreadId() + \"] \" + threadInfo.getThreadName());\n\t\t}\n\t}\n}\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203840-xwrimxn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203840-xwrimxn","updated":"20220906203840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上述程序输出如下（输出内容可能不同，不用太纠结下面每个线程的作用，只用知道 main 线程执行 main 方法即可）：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203841-0xwottm","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906203841-0xwottm","updated":"20220906203841"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"[5] Attach Listener //添加事件\n[4] Signal Dispatcher // 分发处理给 JVM 信号的线程\n[3] Finalizer //调用对象 finalize 方法的线程\n[2] Reference Handler //清除 reference 线程\n[1] main //main 线程,程序入口\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203842-4zuti83","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203842-4zuti83","updated":"20220906203842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从上面的输出内容可以看出：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一个 Java 程序的运行是 main 线程和多个其他线程同时运行"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203843-759gjba","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203843-759gjba","updated":"20220906203843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"请简要描述线程与进程的关系,区别及优缺点？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203844-1v6tfca","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203844-1v6tfca","updated":"20220906203844"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从 JVM 角度说进程和线程之间的关系。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203845-235nxj4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203845-235nxj4","updated":"20220906203845"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"图解进程和线程的关系","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203846-nkrggla","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203846-nkrggla","updated":"20220906203846"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下图是 Java 内存区域，通过下图我们从 JVM 的角度来说一下线程和进程之间的关系。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203847-yta3jft","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203847-yta3jft","updated":"20220906203847"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Java 运行时数据区域（JDK1.8 之后）","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/java/jvm/java-runtime-data-areas-jdk1.8.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203848-h6ss534","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203848-h6ss534","updated":"20220906203848"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从上图可以看出：一个进程中可以有多个线程，多个线程共享进程的","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"堆"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"方法区 (JDK1.8 之后的元空间)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"资源，但是每个线程有自己的","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"程序计数器"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚拟机栈"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"本地方法栈"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203849-3w4w8a0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203849-3w4w8a0","updated":"20220906203849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"总结："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"线程是进程划分成的更小的运行单位。线程和进程最大的不同在于基本上各进程是独立的，而各线程则不一定，因为同一进程中的线程极有可能会相互影响。线程执行开销小，但不利于资源的管理和保护；而进程正相反。"}]},{"ID":"20220906203850-761ffgq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203850-761ffgq","updated":"20220906203850"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面是该知识点的扩展内容！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203851-53rt5de","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203851-53rt5de","updated":"20220906203851"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面来思考这样一个问题：为什么","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"程序计数器"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚拟机栈"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"本地方法栈"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是线程私有的呢？为什么堆和方法区是线程共享的呢？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203852-f22kjpg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203852-f22kjpg","updated":"20220906203852"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"程序计数器为什么是私有的?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203853-fmdo92l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203853-fmdo92l","updated":"20220906203853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"程序计数器主要有下面两个作用：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203854-xwfwh3a","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203854-xwfwh3a","updated":"20220906203854"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203855-xuziuiv","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203855-xuziuiv","updated":"20220906203855"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203856-ptkggdu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203856-ptkggdu","updated":"20220906203856"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"字节码解释器通过改变程序计数器来依次读取指令，从而实现代码的流程控制，如：顺序执行、选择、循环、异常处理。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203857-o2tu7q0","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203857-o2tu7q0","updated":"20220906203857"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203858-u2ixotb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203858-u2ixotb","updated":"20220906203858"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在多线程的情况下，程序计数器用于记录当前线程执行的位置，从而当线程被切换回来的时候能够知道该线程上次运行到哪儿了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203859-1ozo47p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203859-1ozo47p","updated":"20220906203859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需要注意的是，如果执行的是 native 方法，那么程序计数器记录的是 undefined 地址，只有执行的是 Java 代码时程序计数器记录的才是下一条指令的地址。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203860-ozj2xvf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203860-ozj2xvf","updated":"20220906203860"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以，程序计数器私有主要是为了","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"线程切换后能恢复到正确的执行位置"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203861-byfxxr7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203861-byfxxr7","updated":"20220906203861"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚拟机栈和本地方法栈为什么是私有的?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203862-eg9k48g","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203862-eg9k48g","updated":"20220906203862"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203863-fd5bd8l","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203863-fd5bd8l","updated":"20220906203863"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203864-jnxz47x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203864-jnxz47x","updated":"20220906203864"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚拟机栈："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 每个 Java 方法在执行的同时会创建一个栈帧用于存储局部变量表、操作数栈、常量池引用等信息。从方法调用直至执行完成的过程，就对应着一个栈帧在 Java 虚拟机栈中入栈和出栈的过程。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203865-b6dsjyi","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203865-b6dsjyi","updated":"20220906203865"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203866-yy5cfh3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203866-yy5cfh3","updated":"20220906203866"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"本地方法栈："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和虚拟机栈所发挥的作用非常相似，区别是： ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚拟机栈为虚拟机执行 Java 方法 （也就是字节码）服务，而本地方法栈则为虚拟机使用到的 Native 方法服务。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 在 HotSpot 虚拟机中和 Java 虚拟机栈合二为一。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203867-i9p3xuv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203867-i9p3xuv","updated":"20220906203867"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以，为了","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"保证线程中的局部变量不被别的线程访问到"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，虚拟机栈和本地方法栈是线程私有的。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203868-rqj60pe","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203868-rqj60pe","updated":"20220906203868"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一句话简单了解堆和方法区","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203869-4u2fzs8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203869-4u2fzs8","updated":"20220906203869"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"堆和方法区是所有线程共享的资源，其中堆是进程中最大的一块内存，主要用于存放新创建的对象 (几乎所有对象都在这里分配内存)，方法区主要用于存放已被加载的类信息、常量、静态变量、即时编译器编译后的代码等数据。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203870-x2uj29i","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203870-x2uj29i","updated":"20220906203870"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"并发与并行的区别","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203871-ywl5ues","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203871-ywl5ues","updated":"20220906203871"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203872-c9bqfoo","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203872-c9bqfoo","updated":"20220906203872"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203873-131wy5c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203873-131wy5c","updated":"20220906203873"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"并发"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：两个及两个以上的作业在同一 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"时间段"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 内执行。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203874-y9yaltn","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203874-y9yaltn","updated":"20220906203874"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203875-9kt3ypn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203875-9kt3ypn","updated":"20220906203875"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"并行"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：两个及两个以上的作业在同一 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"时刻"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 执行。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203876-pgfxnmp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203876-pgfxnmp","updated":"20220906203876"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最关键的点是：是否是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"同时"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 执行。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203877-t9kd7xo","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203877-t9kd7xo","updated":"20220906203877"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同步和异步的区别","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203878-5lrq06z","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203878-5lrq06z","updated":"20220906203878"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203879-11vmsga","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203879-11vmsga","updated":"20220906203879"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203880-yjfxysi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203880-yjfxysi","updated":"20220906203880"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"同步"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ： 发出一个调用之后，在没有得到结果之前， 该调用就不可以返回，一直等待。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203881-akvvzjq","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203881-akvvzjq","updated":"20220906203881"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203882-2hdzwwo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203882-2hdzwwo","updated":"20220906203882"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"异步"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：调用在发出之后，不用等待返回结果，该调用直接返回。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203883-x28wuu2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203883-x28wuu2","updated":"20220906203883"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为什么要使用多线程呢?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203884-yxgu9p0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203884-yxgu9p0","updated":"20220906203884"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"先从总体上来说：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203885-q64fqfp","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203885-q64fqfp","updated":"20220906203885"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203886-87rswne","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203886-87rswne","updated":"20220906203886"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203887-xzk14yy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203887-xzk14yy","updated":"20220906203887"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"从计算机底层来说："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 线程可以比作是轻量级的进程，是程序执行的最小单位,线程间的切换和调度的成本远远小于进程。另外，多核 CPU 时代意味着多个线程可以同时运行，这减少了线程上下文切换的开销。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203888-4nbf720","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203888-4nbf720","updated":"20220906203888"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203889-nlxmqdb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203889-nlxmqdb","updated":"20220906203889"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"从当代互联网发展趋势来说："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 现在的系统动不动就要求百万级甚至千万级的并发量，而多线程并发编程正是开发高并发系统的基础，利用好多线程机制可以大大提高系统整体的并发能力以及性能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203890-b02ua7s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203890-b02ua7s","updated":"20220906203890"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"再深入到计算机底层来探讨：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203891-ynk1dqz","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203891-ynk1dqz","updated":"20220906203891"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203892-g8pcgr9","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203892-g8pcgr9","updated":"20220906203892"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203893-7qbn27g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203893-7qbn27g","updated":"20220906203893"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"单核时代"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"： 在单核时代多线程主要是为了提高单进程利用 CPU 和 IO 系统的效率。 假设只运行了一个 Java 进程的情况，当我们请求 IO 的时候，如果 Java 进程中只有一个线程，此线程被 IO 阻塞则整个进程被阻塞。CPU 和 IO 设备只有一个在运行，那么可以简单地说系统整体效率只有 50%。当使用多线程的时候，一个线程被 IO 阻塞，其他线程还可以继续使用 CPU。从而提高了 Java 进程利用系统资源的整体效率。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203894-jq1n12o","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203894-jq1n12o","updated":"20220906203894"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203895-u6b7w14","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203895-u6b7w14","updated":"20220906203895"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多核时代"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 多核时代多线程主要是为了提高进程利用多核 CPU 的能力。举个例子：假如我们要计算一个复杂的任务，我们只用一个线程的话，不论系统有几个 CPU 核心，都只会有一个 CPU 核心被利用到。而创建多个线程，这些线程可以被映射到底层多个 CPU 上执行，在任务中的多个线程没有资源竞争的情况下，任务执行的效率会有显著性的提高，约等于（单核时执行时间/CPU 核心数）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203896-hophjy8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203896-hophjy8","updated":"20220906203896"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用多线程可能带来什么问题?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203897-2dyqxnm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203897-2dyqxnm","updated":"20220906203897"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"并发编程的目的就是为了能提高程序的执行效率提高程序运行速度，但是并发编程并不总是能提高程序运行速度的，而且并发编程可能会遇到很多问题，比如：内存泄漏、死锁、线程不安全等等。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203898-rwtny70","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203898-rwtny70","updated":"20220906203898"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"说说线程的生命周期和状态?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203899-bu475mh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203899-bu475mh","updated":"20220906203899"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Java 线程在运行的生命周期中的指定时刻只可能处于下面 6 种不同状态的其中一个状态：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203900-rwezg6p","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203900-rwezg6p","updated":"20220906203900"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203901-yt1orz2","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203901-yt1orz2","updated":"20220906203901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203902-7pjpvmm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203902-7pjpvmm","updated":"20220906203902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"NEW: 初始状态，线程被创建出来但没有被调用 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"start()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203903-75npa45","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203903-75npa45","updated":"20220906203903"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203904-p6kljk1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203904-p6kljk1","updated":"20220906203904"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"RUNNABLE: 运行状态，线程被调用了 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"start()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"等待运行的状态。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203905-9hzfi5o","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203905-9hzfi5o","updated":"20220906203905"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203906-oe61ye0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203906-oe61ye0","updated":"20220906203906"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"BLOCKED ：阻塞状态，需要等待锁释放。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203907-0h5n5v4","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203907-0h5n5v4","updated":"20220906203907"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203908-y1r9jg5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203908-y1r9jg5","updated":"20220906203908"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"WAITING：等待状态，表示该线程需要等待其他线程做出一些特定动作（通知或中断）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203909-sdh59fn","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203909-sdh59fn","updated":"20220906203909"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203910-jjo4bcv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203910-jjo4bcv","updated":"20220906203910"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TIME_WAITING：超时等待状态，可以在指定的时间后自行返回而不是像 WAITING 那样一直等待。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203911-iufp1ar","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203911-iufp1ar","updated":"20220906203911"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203912-5cqk9yn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203912-5cqk9yn","updated":"20220906203912"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TERMINATED：终止状态，表示该线程已经运行完毕。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203913-u08b4k3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203913-u08b4k3","updated":"20220906203913"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程在生命周期中并不是固定处于某一个状态而是随着代码的执行在不同状态之间切换。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203914-93rpz1s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203914-93rpz1s","updated":"20220906203914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Java 线程状态变迁图(图源：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UOrXql_LhOD8dhTq_EPI0w","TextMarkTextContent":"挑错 |《Java 并发编程的艺术》中关于线程状态的三处错误"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":")：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203915-cp1jbl0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203915-cp1jbl0","updated":"20220906203915"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Java 线程状态变迁图","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/java/concurrent/640.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203916-hw0otdw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203916-hw0otdw","updated":"20220906203916"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由上图可以看出：线程创建之后它将处于 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"NEW（新建）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 状态，调用 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"start()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 方法后开始运行，线程这时候处于 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"READY（可运行）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 状态。可运行状态的线程获得了 CPU 时间片（timeslice）后就处于 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"RUNNING（运行）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 状态。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203917-ivh7azm","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906203917-ivh7azm","updated":"20220906203917"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906203918-pausfav","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203918-pausfav","updated":"20220906203918"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在操作系统层面，线程有 READY 和 RUNNING 状态；而在 JVM 层面，只能看到 RUNNABLE 状态（图源：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://howtodoinJava.com/","TextMarkATitle":"HowToDoInJava","TextMarkTextContent":"HowToDoInJava"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://howtodoinJava.com/Java/multi-threading/Java-thread-life-cycle-and-thread-states/","TextMarkATitle":"Java Thread Life Cycle and Thread States","TextMarkTextContent":"Java Thread Life Cycle and Thread States"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"），所以 Java 系统一般将这两个状态统称为 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"RUNNABLE（运行中）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 状态 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203919-srwg949","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203919-srwg949","updated":"20220906203919"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"为什么 JVM 没有区分这两种状态呢？"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" （摘自：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://www.zhihu.com/question/56494969/answer/154053599","TextMarkTextContent":"Java 线程运行怎么有第六种状态？ - Dawell 的回答"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ） 现在的时分（time-sharing）多任务（multi-task）操作系统架构通常都是用所谓的“时间分片（time quantum or time slice）”方式进行抢占式（preemptive）轮转调度（round-robin 式）。这个时间分片通常是很小的，一个线程一次最多只能在 CPU 上运行比如 10-20ms 的时间（此时处于 running 状态），也即大概只有 0.01 秒这一量级，时间片用后就要被切换下来放入调度队列的末尾等待再次调度。（也即回到 ready 状态）。线程切换的如此之快，区分这两种状态就没什么意义了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203920-i3tkxud","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203920-i3tkxud","updated":"20220906203920"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"RUNNABLE-VS-RUNNING","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://my-blog-to-use.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/2019-3/RUNNABLE-VS-RUNNING.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203921-0h0tsnh","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203921-0h0tsnh","updated":"20220906203921"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203922-k9pxh2o","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203922-k9pxh2o","updated":"20220906203922"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203923-q2vfm1c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203923-q2vfm1c","updated":"20220906203923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当线程执行 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"wait()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法之后，线程进入 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"WAITING（等待）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 状态。进入等待状态的线程需要依靠其他线程的通知才能够返回到运行状态。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203924-svyv40u","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203924-svyv40u","updated":"20220906203924"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203925-p9n2pcy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203925-p9n2pcy","updated":"20220906203925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"TIMED_WAITING(超时等待)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 状态相当于在等待状态的基础上增加了超时限制，比如通过 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"sleep（long millis）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法或 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"wait（long millis）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法可以将线程置于 TIMED_WAITING 状态。当超时时间结束后，线程将会返回到 RUNNABLE 状态。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203926-jot8tmk","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203926-jot8tmk","updated":"20220906203926"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203927-2v3ikso","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203927-2v3ikso","updated":"20220906203927"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当线程进入 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"synchronized"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 方法/块或者调用 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"wait"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 后（被 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"notify"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）重新进入 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"synchronized"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 方法/块，但是锁被其它线程占有，这个时候线程就会进入 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"BLOCKED（阻塞）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 状态。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203928-qggmjn1","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203928-qggmjn1","updated":"20220906203928"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203929-b0r8k44","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203929-b0r8k44","updated":"20220906203929"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程在执行完了 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"run()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法之后将会进入到 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"TERMINATED（终止）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 状态。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203930-xu92ex1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203930-xu92ex1","updated":"20220906203930"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相关阅读：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/R5MrTsWvk9McFSQ7bS0W2w","TextMarkTextContent":"线程的几种状态你真的了解么？"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203931-s7bvhj2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203931-s7bvhj2","updated":"20220906203931"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是上下文切换?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203932-j3fdwl6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203932-j3fdwl6","updated":"20220906203932"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程在执行过程中会有自己的运行条件和状态（也称上下文），比如上文所说到过的程序计数器，栈信息等。当出现如下情况的时候，线程会从占用 CPU 状态中退出。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203933-gd7f27o","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203933-gd7f27o","updated":"20220906203933"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203934-uz0cf9h","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203934-uz0cf9h","updated":"20220906203934"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203935-fn0busa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203935-fn0busa","updated":"20220906203935"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主动让出 CPU，比如调用了 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"sleep()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":", ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"wait()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 等。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203936-dzxr3lz","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203936-dzxr3lz","updated":"20220906203936"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203937-i1y9ui9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203937-i1y9ui9","updated":"20220906203937"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间片用完，因为操作系统要防止一个线程或者进程长时间占用 CPU 导致其他线程或者进程饿死。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203938-tefqp8a","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203938-tefqp8a","updated":"20220906203938"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203939-zmnvnci","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203939-zmnvnci","updated":"20220906203939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"调用了阻塞类型的系统中断，比如请求 IO，线程被阻塞。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203940-2nhwjn5","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203940-2nhwjn5","updated":"20220906203940"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203941-tc7zcam","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203941-tc7zcam","updated":"20220906203941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"被终止或结束运行","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203942-xe8xbkp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203942-xe8xbkp","updated":"20220906203942"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这其中前三种都会发生线程切换，线程切换意味着需要保存当前线程的上下文，留待线程下次占用 CPU 的时候恢复现场。并加载下一个将要占用 CPU 的线程上下文。这就是所谓的 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"上下文切换"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203943-0s75jfa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203943-0s75jfa","updated":"20220906203943"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上下文切换是现代操作系统的基本功能，因其每次需要保存信息恢复信息，这将会占用 CPU，内存等系统资源进行处理，也就意味着效率会有一定损耗，如果频繁切换就会造成整体效率低下。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203944-91xw96x","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203944-91xw96x","updated":"20220906203944"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是线程死锁?如何避免死锁?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203945-dhkkfme","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203945-dhkkfme","updated":"20220906203945"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"认识线程死锁","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203946-6c01lqt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203946-6c01lqt","updated":"20220906203946"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程死锁描述的是这样一种情况：多个线程同时被阻塞，它们中的一个或者全部都在等待某个资源被释放。由于线程被无限期地阻塞，因此程序不可能正常终止。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203947-8ufupx9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203947-8ufupx9","updated":"20220906203947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如下图所示，线程 A 持有资源 2，线程 B 持有资源 1，他们同时都想申请对方的资源，所以这两个线程就会互相等待而进入死锁状态。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203948-dg5n7k9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203948-dg5n7k9","updated":"20220906203948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"线程死锁示意图 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://my-blog-to-use.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/2019-4/2019-4%E6%AD%BB%E9%94%811.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203949-y9y3xhf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203949-y9y3xhf","updated":"20220906203949"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面通过一个例子来说明线程死锁,代码模拟了上图的死锁的情况 (代码来源于《并发编程之美》)：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203950-tviotkl","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906203950-tviotkl","updated":"20220906203950"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"public class DeadLockDemo {\n    private static Object resource1 = new Object();//资源 1\n    private static Object resource2 = new Object();//资源 2\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        new Thread(() -\u003e {\n            synchronized (resource1) {\n                System.out.println(Thread.currentThread() + \"get resource1\");\n                try {\n                    Thread.sleep(1000);\n                } catch (InterruptedException e) {\n                    e.printStackTrace();\n                }\n                System.out.println(Thread.currentThread() + \"waiting get resource2\");\n                synchronized (resource2) {\n                    System.out.println(Thread.currentThread() + \"get resource2\");\n                }\n            }\n        }, \"线程 1\").start();\n\n        new Thread(() -\u003e {\n            synchronized (resource2) {\n                System.out.println(Thread.currentThread() + \"get resource2\");\n                try {\n                    Thread.sleep(1000);\n                } catch (InterruptedException e) {\n                    e.printStackTrace();\n                }\n                System.out.println(Thread.currentThread() + \"waiting get resource1\");\n                synchronized (resource1) {\n                    System.out.println(Thread.currentThread() + \"get resource1\");\n                }\n            }\n        }, \"线程 2\").start();\n    }\n}\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203951-82lidfz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203951-82lidfz","updated":"20220906203951"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Output","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203952-dix0c98","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906203952-dix0c98","updated":"20220906203952"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"Thread[线程 1,5,main]get resource1\nThread[线程 2,5,main]get resource2\nThread[线程 1,5,main]waiting get resource2\nThread[线程 2,5,main]waiting get resource1\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203953-kmxc89r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203953-kmxc89r","updated":"20220906203953"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程 A 通过 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"synchronized (resource1)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 获得 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"resource1"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的监视器锁，然后通过","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Thread.sleep(1000);"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"让线程 A 休眠 1s 为的是让线程 B 得到执行然后获取到 resource2 的监视器锁。线程 A 和线程 B 休眠结束了都开始企图请求获取对方的资源，然后这两个线程就会陷入互相等待的状态，这也就产生了死锁。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203954-rio4d3w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203954-rio4d3w","updated":"20220906203954"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上面的例子符合产生死锁的四个必要条件：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203955-qs7kdoh","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203955-qs7kdoh","updated":"20220906203955"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203956-qhm58mu","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203956-qhm58mu","updated":"20220906203956"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203957-pjm83yh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203957-pjm83yh","updated":"20220906203957"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"互斥条件：该资源任意一个时刻只由一个线程占用。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203958-33wl77p","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203958-33wl77p","updated":"20220906203958"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203959-0zffrmm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203959-0zffrmm","updated":"20220906203959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"请求与保持条件：一个线程因请求资源而阻塞时，对已获得的资源保持不放。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203960-r44ovrx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203960-r44ovrx","updated":"20220906203960"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203961-991wv1f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203961-991wv1f","updated":"20220906203961"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不剥夺条件:线程已获得的资源在未使用完之前不能被其他线程强行剥夺，只有自己使用完毕后才释放资源。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203962-qw0uzwi","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NA==","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203962-qw0uzwi","updated":"20220906203962"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203963-ezso00a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203963-ezso00a","updated":"20220906203963"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"循环等待条件:若干线程之间形成一种头尾相接的循环等待资源关系。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203964-gs0q38q","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203964-gs0q38q","updated":"20220906203964"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何预防和避免线程死锁?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203965-hlk5jtc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203965-hlk5jtc","updated":"20220906203965"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"如何预防死锁？"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 破坏死锁的产生的必要条件即可：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203966-nnlp1he","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203966-nnlp1he","updated":"20220906203966"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203967-bjkksor","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203967-bjkksor","updated":"20220906203967"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203968-xmxygcc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203968-xmxygcc","updated":"20220906203968"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"破坏请求与保持条件"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：一次性申请所有的资源。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203969-gzw59lt","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203969-gzw59lt","updated":"20220906203969"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203970-7abg9o6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203970-7abg9o6","updated":"20220906203970"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"破坏不剥夺条件"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：占用部分资源的线程进一步申请其他资源时，如果申请不到，可以主动释放它占有的资源。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203971-qnf8212","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203971-qnf8212","updated":"20220906203971"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203972-qiokx51","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203972-qiokx51","updated":"20220906203972"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"破坏循环等待条件"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：靠按序申请资源来预防。按某一顺序申请资源，释放资源则反序释放。破坏循环等待条件。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203973-cy36kdn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203973-cy36kdn","updated":"20220906203973"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"如何避免死锁？"}]},{"ID":"20220906203974-peuzi3n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203974-peuzi3n","updated":"20220906203974"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"避免死锁就是在资源分配时，借助于算法（比如银行家算法）对资源分配进行计算评估，使其进入安全状态。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203975-ulbjufa","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906203975-ulbjufa","updated":"20220906203975"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906203976-luvdw00","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203976-luvdw00","updated":"20220906203976"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"安全状态"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 指的是系统能够按照某种线程推进顺序（P1、P2、P3.....Pn）来为每个线程分配所需资源，直到满足每个线程对资源的最大需求，使每个线程都可顺利完成。称 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"\u0026lt;P1、P2、P3.....Pn\u0026gt;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 序列为安全序列。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203977-1ffoox3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203977-1ffoox3","updated":"20220906203977"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们对线程 2 的代码修改成下面这样就不会产生死锁了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203978-9erssyg","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906203978-9erssyg","updated":"20220906203978"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"new Thread(() -\u003e {\n            synchronized (resource1) {\n                System.out.println(Thread.currentThread() + \"get resource1\");\n                try {\n                    Thread.sleep(1000);\n                } catch (InterruptedException e) {\n                    e.printStackTrace();\n                }\n                System.out.println(Thread.currentThread() + \"waiting get resource2\");\n                synchronized (resource2) {\n                    System.out.println(Thread.currentThread() + \"get resource2\");\n                }\n            }\n        }, \"线程 2\").start();\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203979-xqnui0l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203979-xqnui0l","updated":"20220906203979"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"输出：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203980-vq0wyzj","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906203980-vq0wyzj","updated":"20220906203980"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"Thread[线程 1,5,main]get resource1\nThread[线程 1,5,main]waiting get resource2\nThread[线程 1,5,main]get resource2\nThread[线程 2,5,main]get resource1\nThread[线程 2,5,main]waiting get resource2\nThread[线程 2,5,main]get resource2\n\nProcess finished with exit code 0\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203981-47g5qkl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203981-47g5qkl","updated":"20220906203981"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们分析一下上面的代码为什么避免了死锁的发生?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203982-hqtwu24","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203982-hqtwu24","updated":"20220906203982"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程 1 首先获得到 resource1 的监视器锁,这时候线程 2 就获取不到了。然后线程 1 再去获取 resource2 的监视器锁，可以获取到。然后线程 1 释放了对 resource1、resource2 的监视器锁的占用，线程 2 获取到就可以执行了。这样就破坏了破坏循环等待条件，因此避免了死锁。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203983-op6lnf0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203983-op6lnf0","updated":"20220906203983"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"sleep() 方法和 wait() 方法对比","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203984-1yoe83h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203984-1yoe83h","updated":"20220906203984"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"共同点"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：两者都可以暂停线程的执行。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203985-p54esse","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203985-p54esse","updated":"20220906203985"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"区别"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203986-i8qnduw","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203986-i8qnduw","updated":"20220906203986"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203987-i6rj389","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203987-i6rj389","updated":"20220906203987"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203988-63g9pvv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203988-63g9pvv","updated":"20220906203988"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong code","TextMarkTextContent":"sleep()"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":" 方法没有释放锁，而 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong code","TextMarkTextContent":"wait()"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":" 方法释放了锁"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203989-jrkglyh","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203989-jrkglyh","updated":"20220906203989"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203990-1x1t8vb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203990-1x1t8vb","updated":"20220906203990"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"wait()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 通常被用于线程间交互/通信，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"sleep()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"通常被用于暂停执行。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203991-oamqjof","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203991-oamqjof","updated":"20220906203991"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203992-arlom4c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203992-arlom4c","updated":"20220906203992"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"wait()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 方法被调用后，线程不会自动苏醒，需要别的线程调用同一个对象上的 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"notify()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"或者 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"notifyAll()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 方法。","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"sleep()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法执行完成后，线程会自动苏醒，或者也可以使用 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"wait(long timeout)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 超时后线程会自动苏醒。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203993-3qs83tk","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203993-3qs83tk","updated":"20220906203993"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203994-2m3l8dp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203994-2m3l8dp","updated":"20220906203994"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"sleep()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Thread"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 类的静态本地方法，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"wait()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 则是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Object"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 类的本地方法。为什么这样设计呢？","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203995-8gwbkkx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203995-8gwbkkx","updated":"20220906203995"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为什么 wait() 方法不定义在 Thread 中？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203996-cvmdho6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203996-cvmdho6","updated":"20220906203996"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"wait()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是让获得对象锁的线程实现等待，会自动释放当前线程占有的对象锁。每个对象（","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Object"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）都拥有对象锁，既然要释放当前线程占有的对象锁并让其进入 WAITING 状态，自然是要操作对应的对象（","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Object"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）而非当前的线程（","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Thread"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203997-ixy3sf9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203997-ixy3sf9","updated":"20220906203997"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类似的问题：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"为什么 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong code","TextMarkTextContent":"sleep()"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"str