ey 为 null 的 Entry。假如我们不做任何措施的话，value 永远无法被 GC 回收，这个时候就可能会产生内存泄露。","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"ThreadLocalMap"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 实现中已经考虑了这种情况，在调用 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"set()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"get()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"remove()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 方法的时候，会清理掉 key 为 null 的记录。使用完 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"ThreadLocal"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法后 最好手动调用","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"remove()"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204189-rj2d859","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906204189-rj2d859","updated":"20220906204189"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"static class Entry extends WeakReference\u003cThreadLocal\u003c?\u003e\u003e {\n    /** The value associated with this ThreadLocal. */\n    Object value;\n\n    Entry(ThreadLocal\u003c?\u003e k, Object v) {\n        super(k);\n        value = v;\n    }\n}\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204190-6ozofct","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204190-6ozofct","updated":"20220906204190"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"弱引用介绍："}]},{"ID":"20220906204191-tk3jp6j","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204191-tk3jp6j","updated":"20220906204191"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204192-9rs3rux","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204192-9rs3rux","updated":"20220906204192"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果一个对象只具有弱引用，那就类似于","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"可有可无的生活用品"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。弱引用与软引用的区别在于：只具有弱引用的对象拥有更短暂的生命周期。在垃圾回收器线程扫描它 所管辖的内存区域的过程中，一旦发现了只具有弱引用的对象，不管当前内存空间足够与否，都会回收它的内存。不过，由于垃圾回收器是一个优先级很低的线程， 因此不一定会很快发现那些只具有弱引用的对象。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204193-v2njccv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204193-v2njccv","updated":"20220906204193"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"弱引用可以和一个引用队列（ReferenceQueue）联合使用，如果弱引用所引用的对象被垃圾回收，Java 虚拟机就会把这个弱引用加入到与之关联的引用队列中。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204194-oxxqvuk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204194-oxxqvuk","updated":"20220906204194"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程池","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204195-66zizqq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204195-66zizqq","updated":"20220906204195"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程池相关的知识点和面试题总结请看这篇文章：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/java/concurrent/java-thread-pool-summary.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Java 线程池详解"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" （由于内容比较多就不放在 PDF 里面了）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"202209062